Ravenna March 12 - 1827 -
"There is some intimate
communion between the
states of the atmosphere in
different systems of the globe.
the double Snipe, the Quail
& the Woodcock never
leave their haunts in
the South till the temp
nature of the month is
fit for them; & this year
the migratory birds are
all late, the snow which
fell in the end of
