257
are seen beautiful villages
with white spires rising
[deletion][unclear]xx[/unclear][/deletion] amongst the trees. [unclear]Man[/unclear]
here seems capable of
enjoying life; animated
nature is gay & inanimate
nature beautiful & sublime
I was received at the house
of a shopkeeper who enter
tains strangers as an Inn=
keeper; I found the beds
good, the Carniola wine
excellent & the Cuisine
